snippet.title: Happy Hacking Keyboard Type S - My Keyboard (SA Keycaps)
snippet.description:
Here's my Happy Hacking Keyboard (hhkb) Type S, lubed and with SA keycaps! I spent lots and lots of time making this hhkb type s even nicer to type on! Likes are greatly appreciated, helps motivate me to make more videos!

Keyboard:
HHKB Type S: https://amzn.to/2U311vn

Accessories:
Lindy Mini USB Cable: https://amzn.to/2HDnzgr
Happy Hacking Carrying Case: https://amzn.to/2Wj8TGE
Glorious Wrist Rest: https://amzn.to/2U5C1na
WASD Keycap Puller: https://amzn.to/2TsMZia
EK MechLube2: https://elitekeyboards.com/products.php?sub=access,misc&pid=mechlube_2

Parts:
Industrial SA Keycaps: https://pimpmykeyboard.com/sa-industrial-keyset/
Topre to MX Cherry Sliders: https://www.aliexpress.com/item/Free-Shipping-Cool-Jazz-Topre-to-MX-adapter-Topre-change-into-MX-switch-into-MX-keycap/32820534494.html?spm=2114.search0104.3.31.66cdb01ctGd3Zr&ws_ab_test=searchweb0_0,searchweb201602_1_10065_10344_10130_10068_10324_10547_10342_10325_10546_10343_10340_10548_10341_10545_10084_10083_10618_10615_10307_10313_10059_10534_100031_10103_441_10624_442_10623_10622_10621_10620_10142,searchweb201603_28,ppcSwitch_5&algo_expid=3cbc193b-b36f-44e0-8c24-01129bb56568-4&algo_pvid=3cbc193b-b36f-44e0-8c24-01129bb56568&transAbTest=ae803_4&priceBeautifyAB=1
3D Printed Sliders for Shift, Enter and Space: https://www.shapeways.com/shops/axiom-1
